  "classificationDefinitions": {
    "SupportedAndModeled": "The first slice consumes the validated shape and applies the named resolver rule.",
    "KnownResolutionNeutral": "The validated field is retained in input identity but cannot alter first-slice source membership, target selection, importer format, package ownership, or public-surface selection under the named reason.",
